docs {
  ## Patch Recipe Category
  อัปเดตบางฟิลด์ของหมวดหมู่สูตรอาหาร เช่น สถานะการใช้งาน โดยไม่แทนที่ข้อมูลทั้งหมด

  Partially updates specific fields of a recipe category without replacing the entire record.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Recipe category ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "name": "Main Course (Patched)",
    "is_active": true
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | Request body fails validation |
  | 401 | Bearer token is missing or invalid |
  | 403 | User lacks recipe category update permission |
  | 404 | Recipe category not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

